prompts.frontCover: Greeting card front cover, minimalist flat 2D vector illustration of a funny beach scene. In the center, cartoon illustrated versions of Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo are comically buried up to their necks in sand. Lao Lao, on the left, has a huge, joyful smile, and Jordan, on the right, has a playful, happy expression. They are wearing their clothes from the photo (plain light blue sweatshirt for Lao Lao, plain tan hoodie for Jordan). Above Lao Lao's head is a small, simple beach umbrella providing her with shade. Above Jordan's head, a cartoon seagull with a mischievous look is attempting to steal a party hat perched on his sandy head. The background is a clean, simple representation of a beach with a minimalist wave line for the ocean and a solid soft blue sky. Centered in the sky above the couple, the words "Happy Birthday Lao Lao" are written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script in a dark sand color. The overall composition is clean, centered, and humorous against a solid light cream background.
